OL,6,FThe States of is under investigation
OL,7,Fafter a data breach resulted in more
OL,8,Fthan 5,000 individuals' records
OL,9,Frelating to health debts being
OL,10,Faccidentally emailed to a customer.
OL,12,FThe data was sent by a civil servant
OL,13,Fwithin the States of Guernsey
OL,14,FCorporate Debt Management Team.
OL,16,FIt contained information including
OL,17,Ffull names and details of amounts owed
OL,18,Ffor service.
