OL,6,FThe email was accidentally sent out on
OL,7,FThursday 18 April by the central
OL,8,FStates of Guernsey Corporate Debt
OL,9,FManagement Team and contained data
OL,10,Frelating to Health & Social Care (HSC)
OL,11,Fliabilities.
OL,13,FIn total, 5,059 individuals are
OL,14,Fthought to have been affected by the
OL,15,Fbreach.
