OL,4,CGuernsey staff member
OL,6,FInformation such as patient names,
OL,7,Freference to and names of parents/
OL,8,Fguardians if the liability related to
OL,9,Fa child, the title of the service, the
OL,10,Fcustomer's unique reference number,
OL,11,Fthe document or invoice number, the
OL,12,Fissue date, the due date and the value
OL,13,Fof the balance was leaked.
OL,15,FHowever, officials have reassured
OL,16,Fmembers of the public saying no
OL,17,Fmedical records or details of
OL,18,Fprocedures were included and that
OL,19,Fthere was no risk of the breach
OL,20,Fleading to identity fraud as
OL,21,Finsufficient data was shared.
