OL,6,FThere were no details relating to
OL,7,Fpersonal income tax, social insurance
OL,8,Fcontributions or corporate tax.
OL,10,FSteps were taken to recover the email
OL,11,Fas soon as the error was noted and the
OL,12,Frecipient also confirmed the email had
OL,13,Fbeen permanently deleted.
OL,15,FChief resources officer Bethan Haines
OL,16,Fsaid: "I know that this incident will
OL,17,Fcause frustration and distress and I
OL,18,Fwant to unreservedly apologise for the
OL,19,Flapse in the security of customer data.
