OL,6,F"The States of Guernsey has strict
OL,7,Finternal training requirements
OL,8,Fspecific to confidentiality and data
OL,9,Fsafeguarding, with refresher training
OL,10,Ffor the Corporate Debt Management Team
OL,11,Foccurring at least annually.
OL,13,F"We take matters of data security
OL,14,Fextremely seriously and have taken
OL,15,Fimmediate steps to strengthen our
OL,16,Fsecurity measures, whilst we continue
OL,17,Fto investigate the incident to capture
OL,18,Fthe lessons learnt."
