OL,7,FAuthority confirmed the matter had
OL,8,Fbeen reported to them.
OL,10,FIn a statement, it said: "The decision
OL,11,Fto initiate this inquiry under section
OL,12,F69 of The Data Protection (Bailiwick
OL,13,Fof Guernsey) Law, 2017 has been made
OL,14,Ffollowing consideration of a breach
OL,15,Fnotification submitted to the
OL,16,FAuthority by the Director of the
OL,17,FRevenue Service and seeks to establish
OL,18,Fwhether the Director of the Revenue
OL,19,FService has breached an operative
OL,20,Fprovision of the Law.
